==Out of the dark==
=== Talking to Mistag ===
* '''Mistag:''' It is good to see you again! The Dorgeshuun Council would like to ask a favour of you, if you are interested?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What is this favour?}}
** '''Player:''' What is this favour?
** '''Mistag:''' Surface-dwellers have been visiting the mines for some time now, but no Dorgeshuun has yet visited the surface.
** '''Mistag:''' We are curious about the surface, and we are also worried about the dangers it poses. We know that Lumbridge is friendly but we are worried that the HAM group may be plotting against us.
** '''Mistag:''' We are planning to send an agent to the surface and we would like you to act as a guide.
** {{tselect|Start the Death to the Dorgeshuun quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'll act as a guide.
*** '''Mistag:''' Thank you!
*** '''Mistag:''' In order to get into the HAM base undetected you will both need to go in disguise. You should get two full sets of HAM robes. Once you have them, our agent will meet you in the cellar of Lumbridge castle.
*** {{tact|previous}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm too busy.
*** '''Mistag:''' Oh dear! Our agent is ready, but the Council will not let an expedition go ahead without a guide. If you reconsider, please let me know!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Can I sell you some ore?}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Why do the Dorgeshuun live underground?}}
* {{topt|quest=no|What happened to your arm?}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Can you show me the way out of the mines?}}

===Talking to Zanik===
* '''Zanik:''' You must be the famous [player name]!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Yes, I'm [player name]!}}
** '''Player:''' Yes, I'm [player name]!
** '''Zanik:''' Pleased to meet you! I'm Zanik of the Dorgeshuun!
** '''Zanik:''' I can't wait to see the surface! But first you need to get us both sets of HAM robes.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Where do I get the robes?}}
*** '''Player:''' Where do I get the robes?
*** '''Zanik:''' How should I know? You're the surface-dweller! Maybe you could steal them from the HAM people or something.
*** '''Zanik:''' We'll need two sets of full robes: shirt, robe, hood, cloak, gloves, boots and badge.
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|Aren't you scared of the surface?}}
*** '''Player:''' Aren't you scared of the surface?
*** '''Zanik:''' Well... a bit. All our legends say it's a terrible place.
*** '''Zanik:''' But that's a bad reason not to visit it. Maybe the legends are wrong. Or even if they're right, we should know for sure.
*** '''Zanik:''' And I've always wondered... what's beyond the next cave? What's at the end of every tunnel? The surface is a whole new world to explore, and I can't wait!
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|What's that mark on your forehead?}}
*** '''Player:''' What's that mark on your forehead?
*** '''Zanik:''' I, er, er...
*** '''Zanik:''' To be honest I don't know. It happened when...
*** '''Zanik:''' If you don't mind, I'd rather not talk about it now. Maybe once you've shown me some of the surface.
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{topt|cond=After choosing at least one dialogue option:|OK}}
*** '''Player:''' OK.
*** '''Zanik:''' See you soon!
*** {{tact|end}}
